Theme 3.0.0

	* [Bug] Install all custom assets, not just registered ones.  Fixes Bug #1520
	* [Feature] #1074 New support for theme-based configuration options and all the supplemental code for
	  them!
	* Standardize some namespace functions and migrate all SESSION operations to \Core\Session.
	* Move the custom css tutorial so it makes sense if the directory doesn't exist yet.
	* Add custom print styles for overriding print-only styles from the theme editor!
	* Cleaned up the interface for managing custom styles on the theme and made the interface more
	  user-friendly.
